snippet.title: Tamarak Trail - Official Gameplay Overview Trailer | The Mix Showcase March 2023
snippet.description: Learn about the corruption plaguing the land, meet the characters, and take a look at combat in this deep-dive look at Tamarak Trail, an upcoming turn-based dice-rolling roguelike where you customize dice with powerful abilities and explore a dangerous forest filled with events and monsters. Tamarak Trail is coming in 2023.
